mixin expandable-grid(columns, initialRows=2, items=[])  
  .expandable-grid(data-columns=columns data-initial-rows=initialRows)  
    .expandable-grid__inner  
      each item, index in items  
        .expandable-grid__item= item || `Item ${index + 1}`  
    button.expandable-grid__toggle(type="button") Показать ещё  